title: Cam Newton Opportunity? The best game in NFL Week 2, The Raiders are real, and the Fabulous Five Rookies
itunes:title: Cam Newton Opportunity? The best game in NFL Week 2, The Raiders are real, and the Fabulous Five Rookies
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Peter Schrager, Kyle Brandt, and Thomas Davis start previewing Thursday Night Football. Cam Newton's phone could be ringing soon with an opportunity to play. We also get Fantasy Football strategy in Which Guy Wednesday and Peter's Fabulous Five Rookies.


The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.
